      "review_count": 14,
      "average_rating": 4.21,
      "html": "<div id=\"tab-reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--reviews panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div id=\"reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Reviews\"><div id=\"comments\"><h2 class=\"woocommerce-Reviews-title\">14 reviews for <span>Vyntech S16 5G 90Hz Watch</span></h2><ol class=\"commentlist\">\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1501\">\n<div id=\"comment-1501\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15a?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Aditya K.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Bhai display 90hz hone se kya smooth chalta hai! Super AMOLED display colors are very punchy and deep. Best Android watch under this budget.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/1760279682__17602793122068838925021119333767__original.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1502\">\n<div id=\"comment-1502\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15b?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Suresh Nair</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>180 degree rotatable camera is very unique. Good for video calls on WhatsApp. Taking 1 star off because continuous 5G usage drains the battery a bit fast.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/1764157678__1764157676188-whatsappimage2025-11-26at5__original.jpeg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1503\">\n<div id=\"comment-1503\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15c?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Priya Singh</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Here is my own review for this product: what I found. Initially my delivery was stuck and standard support agent didn't respond properly. I mailed the head contact help.vyntech@gmail.com and the issue was solved instantly! Got my watch next morning. The product is a beast.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/1764157740__1764157738028-whatsappimage2025-11-26at5__original.jpeg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1504\">\n<div id=\"comment-1504\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15d?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Manoj D.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Installed heavy games directly from PlayStore. 2GB RAM handles it well but watch back gets warm after 20 mins of gaming.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Manoj,<br><br>Thank you for the feedback! Please note that slight warming is completely normal during intense 3D gaming due to the powerful processor packed in a compact smartwatch chassis. It is completely safe. For any calibration support, please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1505\">\n<div id=\"comment-1505\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15e?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Venkatesh R.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Chala bagundi. Real standalone Android watch. 32GB storage is great for saving offline Spotify songs for my gym sessions.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/1764157981__1764157971460-whatsappimage2025-11-26at5__original.jpeg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1506\">\n<div id=\"comment-1506\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15f?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 1 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:20%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">1</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Arif Khan</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Display is awesome but the wireless charger provided in the box is defective. It's not charging the watch. Have initiated a replacement.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Arif,<br><br>We really apologize for the inconvenience caused by the defective charger. You need not worry, your replacement request has been approved. A brand new sealed charger will be delivered to you at the time of pickup.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1507\">\n<div id=\"comment-1507\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15g?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Karthik S.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Romba nalla irukku. Full Android OS on wrist feels like magic. Very responsive touch and the camera is surprisingly clear.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/1764158233__1764158230117-whatsappimage2025-11-26at5__original.jpeg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1508\">\n<div id=\"comment-1508\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15h?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Sneha R.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Perfect for daily use, but speaker volume during outdoor calls could be a bit louder. The 32GB space is a lifesaver.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/1764854369__1764854352968-1000060042__original.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1509\">\n<div id=\"comment-1509\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15i?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Gaurav T.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Sometimes WhatsApp notifications don't come in the background until I open the app. Have to manually sync it.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Gaurav,<br><br>We apologize for the inconvenience. This happens due to the Android OS strict battery optimization settings. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and our software support expert will guide you on how to lock the app in the background for seamless push notifications.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1510\">\n<div id=\"comment-1510\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15j?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Tushar Sharma</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>IP67 is genuine. Was caught in light rain while riding my bike and watch is completely fine.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1511\">\n<div id=\"comment-1511\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15k?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Rakesh Patel</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Delivery was delayed by 3 days. But Vyntech support was helpful. Watch is genuinely good, 90hz makes a big difference.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1512\">\n<div id=\"comment-1512\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15l?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Nitin Verma</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Ek number watch hai. Calling feature works flawlessly without phone. Best smartwatch purchase.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1513\">\n<div id=\"comment-1513\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15m?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Amit B.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Totally worth the money. Video calling from wrist feels like a sci-fi movie. Camera quality is top notch.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1514\">\n<div id=\"comment-1514\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/15n?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Deepak J.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\" datetime=\"2026-04-26T09:00:00+00:00\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>The UI is very fast, battery easily lasts the whole day if I use WiFi instead of 5G constantly.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n</ol></div><div class=\"clear\"></div></div></div>"
